snippet.title: Coronation Steam Trailer v2
snippet.description:
Coronation is an online open-world castle builder game where you design fortified castles to withstand attacks from AI or players, keep its people happy, well-fed and rested, or even decorate it to impress curators and provide beautiful homes for accommodation.

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1649920/Coronation/
